00:24:49,940 --> 00:24:50,900
Pass me the bowl.

274
00:25:05,780 --> 00:25:06,620
Is it enough for you?

275
00:25:07,380 --> 00:25:08,740
Yes, sure.

276
00:25:14,820 --> 00:25:16,500
Four relics of ill omen subdued,

277
00:25:17,740 --> 00:25:19,060
yet five stars lit.

